<div id="task-description">
    <h2>Task description</h2>
    You will be asked to join a Zoom call to collaborate with another
    participant in an object search task. You will each be given a role:
    assistant or leader. If you are the assistant, you will go to a
    website where you can control a robot in an environment. If you are
    the leader, you will talk with the assistant to move the robot
    around the environment to find a target object. Your goal is to find
    the object as quickly as possible.
</div>

<div id="agreement">

    <h2>Agreement</h2>
    By agreeing to take part in the task, you are consenting to the
    recording of the Zoom call, which includes the audio, your assigned
    Zoom name, and the text transcription of your conversation. Your
    video will be turned off and NOT recorded. We will also record the
    robotâ€™s movement, and the demographic information you are providing
    below. You will not be able to participate in the task without
    signing this agreement.
</div>


<div class="form-group form-check" id="form-agree-check">
    <input type="checkbox" class="form-check-input" id="agree-check" required>
    <label class="form-check-label" for="agree-check">I agree </label>
</div>
<hr>

<div class="form-group" id="data-fields">
    <div class="form-group" id="age-input">
        <label for="age">Age</label>
        <div class="custom-control custom-radio">
            <input type="radio" class="custom-control-input" id="age-less-20" value="<20" name="age">
            <label class="custom-control-label" " for="age-less-20"><20</label>
        </div>

        <div class="custom-control custom-radio">
            <input type="radio" class="custom-control-input" id="age-20-29" value="20-29" name="age">
            <label class="custom-control-label" for="age-20-29">20-29</label>
        </div>

        <div class="custom-control custom-radio">
            <input type="radio" class="custom-control-input" id="age-30-39" value="30-39" name="age">
            <label class="custom-control-label" for="age-30-39">30-39</label>
        </div>

        <div class="custom-control custom-radio">
            <input type="radio" class="custom-control-input" id="age-40-49" value="40-49" name="age">
            <label class="custom-control-label" for="age-40-49">40-49</label>
        </div>

        <div class="custom-control custom-radio">
            <input type="radio" class="custom-control-input" id="age-50-59" value="50-59" name="age">
            <label class="custom-control-label" for="age-50-59">50-59</label>
        </div>

        <div class="custom-control custom-radio">
            <input type="radio" class="custom-control-input" id="age-60+" value="60+" name="age">
            <label class="custom-control-label" for="age-60+">60+</label>
        </div>

    </div>

    <div class="form-group" id="gender-input">
        <label for="gender">Gender</label>
        <div class="custom-control custom-radio">
            <input type="radio" class="custom-control-input" id="gender-female" value="female" name="gender">
            <label class="custom-control-label" " for="gender-female">Female</label>
        </div>

        <div class="custom-control custom-radio">
            <input type="radio" class="custom-control-input" id="gender-male" value="male" name="gender">
            <label class="custom-control-label" for="gender-male">Male</label>
        </div>

        <div class="custom-control custom-radio">
            <input type="radio" class="custom-control-input" id="gender-other" value="other" name="gender">
            <label class="custom-control-label" for="gender-other">Other</label>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="form-group" id="new-player-input">
        <label for="newPlayer">Is this your first time?</label>
        <div class="custom-control custom-radio">
            <input type="radio" class="custom-control-input" id="new-yes" value="new-yes" name="newPlayer">
            <label class="custom-control-label" for="new-yes">Yes</label>
        </div>

        <div class="custom-control custom-radio">
            <input type="radio" class="custom-control-input" id="new-no" value="new-no" name="newPlayer">
            <label class="custom-control-label" for="new-no">No</label>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
